description: Please note that a 3-year moving-average merge of CPS data is required in order to reduce sampling errors to create comparable state estimates.  These estimates were constructed using years 2008-2010.

metadata.description: Individuals are identified as disabled if they self-reported having a health problem or a disability which prevents work or which limits the kind or amount of work they can perform.

name: Measure 13 : Percentage of the Nonelderly Population with Health Insurance Coverage by Disability Status
